APR FC ihangayikishijwe n'imyigaragambyo ya 'Guma mu Rugo'
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'inzego z'ibanze bavuze ko bagomba guhindura imikorere y'inzego z'ibanze (Ifoto/Umuvugizi w'Umukuru w'Igihugu).
Ibi ngo byatewe n'uko bagiye guhindura izina ry'abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko.
Impungenge za politike zishobora gutuma abantu baseka.
Umwe mu bakozi ba AM yavuze ko itsinda rye "rifite impungenge z'uko rikorana na Twp na Pwp."
Abasomyi bo hanze ya Wales: Muri Welsh Twp bisobanuye ubujura na Pwp bisobanura poo.
Umuvugizi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubumwe bw'Abaturage yatangaje ko "ntibyari bishimishije" kandi ko hari n'ibindi byari byarateguwe.
Umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'igihugu cya Welsh yavuze ko itsinda rye "rifite impungenge" ku bijyanye n'impinduka y'izina, ariko yavuze ko ari impinduka ngufi kuva kuri MWP kugera kuri Muppet.
Muri iyi nyandiko, Ibaruwa y'uwitwa W.S. yanditswe mu rurimi rw'Icyongereza rwitwa Yorkshire.
Komisiyo y'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko, ubu irimo gutegura itegeko ryo gutangaza impinduka z'amazina, yagize iti "Icyemezo cya nyuma ku badepite b'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko icyo ari cyo cyose cyitwa ni ikibazo cy'abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ubwabo."
Itegeko Nshinga ry'umwaka wa 2017/2018 ryahaye Abanyarwanda ububasha bwo guhindura izina ryabo.
Muri Kamena uyu mwaka, Komisiyo yatangaje ibyavuye mu biganiro byatanzwe n'abaturage ku birebana n'inama y'inama y'abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko igamije gushyigikira Inteko Ishinga Amategeko.
Ku bijyanye n'amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu, Komisiyo y'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'u Rwanda yashimangiye abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko cyangwa abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko, ariko amatora ya MWP yahawe inkunga ikomeye mu nama y'abaturage.
Ambs zivuga ko hari amahitamo anyuranye, ariko urugamba rwo kugera ku masezerano rushobora kuba ari ikibazo cy'umutwe w'umukuru w'igihugu, Elin Jones, uteganyijwe gushyiraho amategeko agenga impinduka mu byumweru bishize.
Itegeko rigenga ivugurura rikubiyemo n'impinduka zijyanye n'ibikorwa by'ishyirahamwe, harimo n'amategeko agenga ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'itegeko nshinga, hamwe n'imiterere ya komite.
APR FC igiye gusobanurira abaturage icyo bakwiye gukora mu gihe bazaba bagiye gutora.
Abaturage bo muri Macedonia bagiye gutora mu matora yo guhindura izina ry'igihugu
Ku Cyumweru, Abadepite bagiye gutora niba bazahindura izina ry'igihugu cyabo bakarihindura "Repubulika y'Amajyaruguru ya Macedoniya."
Aya matora yashyizweho mu rwego rwo gukemura amakimbirane y'imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo n'u Bugereki buturanye, bufite intara yabwo bwite yitwa Macedonia.
Athens yakomeje avuga ko izina ry'umuturanyi wayo mu majyaruguru y'amajyaruguru ari ikimenyetso cy'ubusabane mu karere kayo, kandi ko inshuro nyinshi yamaganye ubushake bwayo bw'ubumwe bw'ibihugu bigize EU na NATO.
Perezida wa Macedonia, Gjorge Ivanov, warwanyaga iryo tegeko ryo guhindura izina, yavuze ko atazitabira amatora.
Ariko abashyigikiye referendum, harimo na Minisitiri w'Intebe Zoran Zaev, bavuze ko impinduka y'izina ari ikiguzi cyo kwishyura kugira ngo yinjire muri EU na NATO.
Imyigaragambyo y'abasenyeri b'i Kibeho mu Karere ka Gasabo ikomeje kuba nk'uko byari bimeze mu mirwano ya Harlem
Yagize ati "Mu mateka, abantu bakuru naganiriyeho bavuga ko hari umusenyeri n'idini muri buri murenge.
"Uyu munsi nta n'imwe ihari."
Yakomeje avuga ko gusenyuka kw'amabuye y'agaciro byari bifite ishingiro.
Yagize ati "Abaturage muri iki gihe batandukanye n'abandi.
Ati "Abaturage ntabwo bakiri mu cyumba cy'abaturanyi basanzwe bakoreramo.
Yagize ati "Ikibazo cy'amafaranga y'u Rwanda ntabwo kizamara igihe cyose abayobozi bategereje ko aya mafaranga azatangwa, kandi vuba cyangwa nyuma bazagaruka aho yatangiriye."
Yongeyeho ko amasengero ashobora gusimburwa n'inyubako z'amazu y'ibigo by'amagorofa yuzuyemo abantu badashobora gufasha abaturanyi basigaye.
Yagize ati "Benshi mu bantu bagura amasengero muri izi nyubako bazaba abazungu, kandi ni yo mpamvu bagiye kwihutisha umunsi aya madini yose kuko bidashoboka ko abenshi muri abo bantu binjira muri aya masengero bazahinduka abagize ayo matorero."
Amatorero yombi yubatswe n'amatorero y'abazungu mbere y'uko Harlem ahinduka umujyi w'abirabura - Metropolitan Community mu 1870, nyuma y'imyaka icumi.
Itorero ry'abametodiste b'abazungu ryatangiye mu myaka ya 1930.
Itorero ry'umwirabura ryari ryarasengeye hafi y'iryo torero ryahawe izina ry'uruharo.
St. Martin yafashwe n'itorero ry'abirabura ryo munsi ya Rev. John Howard Johnson, wayoboraga imyigaragambyo y'abacuruzi ku muhanda wa 125, umuhanda ukomeye wo gucuruza i Harlem, warwanyaga gukodesha cyangwa guteza imbere abirabura.
Mu 1939, umuriro wavuye muri iyo nyubako wangiritse cyane, ariko nk'uko Padiri Johnson wa Paruwasi ya Johnson yagize intego yo kubaka, bashyizeho itegeko ryo kubaka carillon.
Rev. David Johnson, umuhungu wa Papa Johnson n'umusimbura muri St Martin, yise "imyenda y'abakene."
Umuhanga wakiniye Carillon muri Nyakanga yabyise ikindi kintu: "Ubutunzi bw'umuco" n' "igikoresho cy'amateka kitazibagirana."
Umuhanga witwa Tiffany Ng wo muri kaminuza ya Michigan, yavuze ko ari wo muhanzi wa mbere ku isi wakiniwe n'umuhanzi w'umwirabura, Dionisio A. Lind, wimukiye muri carillon nini muri Kiliziya ya Riverside mu myaka 18 ishize.
Bwana Merriweather yavuze ko St Martin atamusimbuye.
Mu mezi make ashize, icyo yakinnye muri St Martin cyari inkuru igoye y'abahanga n'abakora ibikoresho, zimwe zazanywe n'abayobozi ba kiliziya, abandi na Diyosezi ya Episcopal.
Mu kwezi kwa Nyakanga, inteko nyobozi ya Paruwasi, igizwe n'abayobozi b'inzego z'ibanze, yanditse iyi diyosezi ifite impungenge ko iyo diyosezi "yagombaga gushakisha ibiciro" kuri iyo nzu, nubwo iyo myenda yari itagize uruhare mu gucunga inyubako n'amasezerano yoherejwe muri iyo dayoseze.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'inzego z'ibanze bitabiriye iki gitaramo bavuze ko babuze ubwisanzure mu itangazamakuru.
Shark yakomerekeje umwana w'imyaka 13 ku rubyiniro rwa Lobster muri California
Ku wa gatandatu, hari shark yagabye igitero ikakomeretsa umwana w'umuhungu w'imyaka 13, ubwo yari yirukanywe i Lobster muri Kaliforniya ku munsi wa mbere w'ikiruhuko.
Icyo gitero cyabaye saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba, hafi y'umujyi wa Beacon mu mujyi wa Encinitas.
Chad Hammel yabwiye KSWB-TV i San Diego ko yamaze hafi isaha n'igice mu gitondo cyo kuri uyu wa Gatandatu ubwo yumvaga uwo muhungu asaba ubufasha maze afatanyije n'itsinda rimufasha kumukura mu mazi.
Hammel yatangiye avuga ko byari ibyishimo gusa, ariko yahise avuga ati: "Yabonye ko yaguye mu mutego!
Bye bye bit!"
Habyarimana yagize ati "Ikibazo cyose cyari cyaracitse."
Agira ati "Nahamagaye abantu bose ngo basohoke mu mazi ngo: 'Hari ingwe mu mazi!'"
Uyu mwana yajyanywe mu bitaro by'i Rady's Children's Hospital i San Diego aho yari arwaye cyane.
Ntabwo haramenyekana ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zatewe n'icyo gitero.
Larry Giles, mu kiganiro yagiranye n'itangazamakuru, yavuze ko hari hashize ibyumweru bike hagaragaye ingwe muri ako gace, ariko ntibyari bizwi ko ari ubwoko bw'inyamaswa.
Gilles yongeyeho ko uwo muntu yakomerekejwe n'ibikomere byakomerekeje mu gace yari atuyemo ko hejuru.
Abayobozi b'inzego z'ibanze bafashe icyemezo cyo kwinjira ku nkombe z'inyanja bava i Ponto Beach muri Casablad bajya i Ecinitas muri Swami amasaha 48 kugira ngo bakore iperereza n'umutekano.
Avuga ko hari ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zirenga 135 muri ako gace, ariko abenshi ntibafatwa nk'aho ari akaga.
Sainsbury yinjiye mu isoko ry'ubwiza bw'u Bwongereza
Sainsbury arimo gutwara Boots, Superdrug na Debenhams, hamwe n'ubwiza bw'ibikoresho by'amaduka bushimishije abakozi bakorana n'abajyanama b'ikoranabuhanga.
Nk'igice cy'umusaruro ukomeye mu isoko ry'ubwiza bw'u Bwongereza <0xC2><0xA3> 2.8bn, ukomeje gukura mu gihe imiterere n'ibicuruzwa by'inzu bigabanuka, ibice binini by'ubwiza bizasuzumwa mu maduka 11 hirya no hino mu gihugu maze bijyanwe mu maduka menshi umwaka utaha.
Ubwishingizi bw'ubwiza buturuka ku masoko akomeye ashakisha uburyo bwo gukoresha ikirere cya shelf igihe cyari gifunzwe kuri televiziyo, microwaves na homeware.
Sainsbury yavuze ko bizagabanya ubunini bw'ibicuruzwa byayo bigera kuri 3,000, harimo n'ibikoresho nka Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman na Dr. PawPaw.
Inyubako zitandukanye zirimo L'Oreal, Maylline na Burt's Bees nazo zizabona ikibanza kinini n'uturere tumeze nk'utundi ducuruzwa tuboneka mu maduka nka Boots.
Iri soko kandi rituma ibicuruzwa byaryo byiyongera ku buryo ibicuruzwa hafi ya byose bigenda byiyongera - ibisabwa n'abakiriya bakiri bato.
Mu cyumweru gishize, umucuruzi w'ibinure azasuzuma ibicuruzwa bya Fragrance mu maduka abiri ya Sainsbury, aya mbere yafunguwe i Croydon, mu majyepfo y'umujyi wa Londres, mu gihe uwa kabiri yafunguye i Selly Oak muri Birmingham, nyuma y'uyu mwaka.
Gucuruza kuri interineti no kugura ibiryo bike buri munsi mu maduka yoroheje, bisaba gukora byinshi kugira ngo abantu basubireyo.
Mike Coupe, umuyobozi mukuru wa Sainsbury, yavuze ko izo nzego zizagenda zigaragara nk'amaduka y'inzego z'ibanze nk'uko ibicuruzwa bya supermarket bigerageza guhangana na Aldi na Lidl bafite serivisi zirenzeho n'ibiribwa.
Sainsbury yashyize ibicuruzwa bya Argos mu maduka amagana kandi yaje no kuzana ibicuruzwa byinshi kuva yagura iminyururu yombi mu myaka ibiri ishize, avuga ko ibicuruzwa by'ibiryo byakomeje gucuruzwa kandi bitanga umusaruro.
Ikibazo cy'ibikorwa by'ubuhinzi n'ubworozi cyari kimaze iminsi kigabanuka mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana n'ibikorwa by'ubuhinzi.
Sainsbury yagerageje ubufatanye na Boots mu ntangiriro z'imyaka ya 2000, ariko urukingo rwarangiritse nyuma y'urukurikirane rw'uburyo bwo gutandukanya amafaranga n'ibicuruzwa bya chemist mu maduka yayo.
Iyi gahunda nshya ije nyuma y'uko Sainsbury yagurishije ubucuruzi bwayo bwa 281 bucuruzwa muri Celesio, nyiri uruganda rwa Lloyds Pharmacy, ku mafaranga miliyoni 125 z'amapawundi mu myaka itatu ishize.
Yakomeje avuga ko ibigo by'imari byari bifite uruhare runini muri iyi gahunda, mu kongera ibicuruzwa byinshi birimo La Roche-Posay na Vichy mu maduka ane.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umuyobozi w'ubucuruzi Sainsbury, yagize ati: "Twahinduye isura n'ibyiyumvo by'ubwiza bwacu kugira ngo duteze imbere ibidukikije.
Nanone kandi, twagiye dutanga inama ku bakozi basanzwe batanga ubufasha.
Ati "Ibicuruzwa byacu byateguwe kugira ngo bihuze n'ibikenewe byose, n'ahantu haryoshye n'ahantu hashimishije, bisobanura ko ubu turi ahantu heza hateye impungenge mu buryo bwo gucuruza ibicuruzwa."
Peter Jones 'yarakajwe' nyuma y'uko Holly Willoughby yirukanye amasezerano ya miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi
Dragons Den star Peter Jones yavuye mu 'bushangashirwe' nyuma y'uko Holly Willoughby yasohoye miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi ajyanye n'ubucuruzi bwe bw'imibereho kugira ngo yibande ku masezerano mashya ya Marks na Spencer na ITV
Diane Rwigara nta mwanya afite wo gushyira mu bikorwa imikino n'imikino y'amagare.
Ubucuruzi bw'aba bombi bwagereranywaga n'ubwa Goop ya Gwyneth Paltrow.
Uyu muhanzi w'imyaka 37 y'amavuko yashyize kuri Instagram yemeza ko agiye gusohoka.
Holly Willoughby yasize Dragons "Den Star Peter Jones anywa itabi mu gukuramo ubucuruzi bwe bw'imibereho myiza ku munota wa nyuma - kwibanda ku masezerano ye mashya ya bumper na Marks <0x26> Spencer na ITV.
Ibitangazamakuru bigaragaza ko Jones "yari afite ubwoba" ubwo umukobwa wa zahabu we yemeraga mu nama ikomeye kuri televiziyo ku wa Kabiri ku cyicaro gikuru cy'ubucuruzi bwe i Marlow, Buckinghamshire, avuga ko amasezerano ye mashya - agera kuri miliyoni 1.5 z'amapawundi - byasobanuraga ko atagifite umwanya uhagije wo kwishyura imyenda yabo yo mu rugo n'ibikoresho.
Ubu bucuruzi bwari bwagereranijwe na Goop ya Gwyneth Paltrow kandi bwari bufite agaciro ka miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi ya Willoughby.
Nk'uko Willoughby w'imyaka 37 y'amavuko yabitangaje kuri Instagram, Jones yavuye mu Bwongereza ajya mu biruhuko.
Umwe muri bo yagize ati "Mu by'ukuri byari ibintu by'ingenzi bya mbere mu buzima bwa Hollywood.
Uyu musore yari agiye kumubona mu myaka mike iri imbere.
Umwanzuro we wo kwirukana abantu bose bari bafitanye ubwumvikane buke.
Nta muntu n'umwe washoboraga kwemera ibyabaye kuri uyu wa Kabiri, kuko byari bifitanye isano n'ibikorwa by'iyi kipe.
Inzu y'ubucuruzi ifite ibicuruzwa byinshi birimo ibicuruzwa by'amashanyarazi birimo ibicuruzwa."
Impuguke zivuga ko kuva muri uyu mutangabuhamya w'iki gitondo, uri mu banki nyinshi mu Bwongereza, bishobora kwishyura miliyoni nyinshi z'iki kigo bitewe n'ishoramari rikomeye mu bicuruzwa bivanye ku macupa n'amatara ku myambarire n'imyenda yo mu rugo, ndetse n'ubushobozi bwo kurushaho gutegereza kugera ku ntangiriro yayo.
Bishobora gusobanura iherezo ry'ubucuti bw'igihe kirekire.
Mama Willoughby n'umugabo we Dan Baldwin bamaze imyaka 10 bakundana na Jones hamwe n'umugore we Tara Capp.
Willoughby yatangiye gukorana na Capp mu 2016 na Jones w'imyaka 52, yinjiye muri Werurwe.
Abashakanye bizihiza umunsi mukuru, Jones afite 40<0x25> by'umusaruro muri sosiyete ya Baldwin TV.
Willoughby azaba ambasaderi wa M<0x26>S kandi azasimbura Ant McPartlin nk'umunyamuryango wa ITV.
Umwe mu bakozi batandukanye yagize ati "Ijoro rishize ntitwavuze ku bijyanye n'ubucuruzi bwe."
