Indonesia: Tsunami n'umutingito byahitanye abantu benshi
Urugero, nyuma y’umutingito wa Lombok, amashyirahamwe y’amahanga atari ay’ubutegetsi yabwiwe ko atari ngombwa.
N'ubwo abarenga 10<0x25> by'abaturage ba Lombok bari baratawe muri yombi, nta mpanuka y'igihugu yatangajwe, hakenewe ubufasha mpuzamahanga.
Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga yagize ati: "Ikibabaje ni uko mu bihe byinshi bagaragaje ko badasaba ubufasha mpuzamahanga, bityo bikaba bigoye cyane."
N'ubwo abayobozi b'inzego z'ibanze bagiye gushyiraho itsinda ry'abayobozi b'ibigo by'imari, ntiharamenyekana niba hari abakora imyitozo ngororamubiri.
Bwana Sutopo, umuvugizi w'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ibiza, yavuze ko abategetsi ba Indonesia bari gusuzuma imimerere iri i Palu kugira ngo barebe niba inzego mpuzamahanga zemeye gutanga imfashanyo.
Kubera ko igihugu cya Indonesia gikomeje guhindagurika, igihugu kiracyari mu mubabaro kubera uburakari bw'ibidukikije.
N'ubwo mu Karere ka Nyabihu hamaze kubakwa ibigo by'itumanaho, ntibyakunze kugaragara mu bindi bice by'umujyi wa Kigali.
Kubura umuburo wa tsunami mu mujyi wa Palu, nubwo byari bimeze bityo, birashoboka ko byagize uruhare mu gutakaza ubuzima.
Mu bihe byiza cyane, urugendo hagati y'ibirwa byinshi byo muri Indonesia ruracyari urujijo.
Impanuka ziterwa n’ibiza zituma impanuka zirushaho kugorana.
Ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bwahagaze i Lombok kugira ngo buvure abantu bazize umutingito bujya i Palu, ariko buzafata nibura iminsi itatu kugira ngo bugere aho iki cyorezo gishya.
Perezida wa Indonesia, Joko Widodo, yashyizeho uburyo bwo kurushaho kongera umusaruro w'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga byo muri Indonesia nk'igice cy'ibanze cy'imyigaragambyo y'amatora, kandi yashyize amafaranga mu mihanda n'amagare.
Ariko ubukene bw'amafaranga bwatumye Perezida Joko asubira mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu mu mwaka utaha.
Bwana Joko kandi ahangayikishijwe n'amakimbirane ashingiye ku mibonano mpuzabitsina muri Indonesia, aho abenshi mu bayisilamu bashyigikiye ubwoko bw'imyizerere.
Abantu barenga igihumbi bishwe, n’abandi babarirwa mu bihumbi bavanwa mu ngo zabo mu gihe amatsinda y’abakirisitu n’abayisilamu yarwanye mu mihanda, akoresheje imiheto, imiheto n’imyampi n’ibindi birwanisho by’iterabwoba.
Liverpool: Umukinnyi wa Liverpool Daniel Sturridge yatsinze umukinnyi wa Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge yakingiye Liverpool kuva muri Premier League atsindwa na Chelsea ku munota wa 89 ku wa Gatandatu i Stamford Bridge i Londres.
Sturridge yavuye muri Xherdan Shaqiri mu gihe yari avuye muri Chelsea afite urugendo rw'amasegonda 30 n'ikipe ye ikurikirana 1-0.
Yahise afata umupira w'inyuma mbere y'uko afata umupira w'inyuma.
Iri rushanwa ryageze hejuru y'uruzitiro kuko ryageze ku ruhande rw'iburyo rw'urukuta.
Amaherezo umupira watsinze Kepa Aririzabazaga maze ugwa mu muvuduko.
Sturridge yabwiye Liverpool.com ati: "Byari bigamije kugera kuri uwo mwanya, gukina umupira n'abakinnyi nka Shaq buri gihe bakina imbere uko bishoboka kose, ku buryo nagerageje kwirema umwanya munini ushoboka."
"Nabonye Kante aje, afata igice kinini cy'umutwe, nta cyo natekerejeho, gusa yahise afata imbunda."
Chelsea yakinnye igitego cya 1-0 ku munota wa 25 nyuma yo gutsinda igitego cya Eden Hazard wo mu Bubiligi.
Umukinnyi w'umupira w'amaguru Blues yasubije Mateo Kovacic kuri uwo mukino, mbere yo gusimbuka hafi y'igice cya Liverpool.
Kovacic yahise atanga igikombe cy'irushanwa muri Midfield.
Yahise yirukana umupira w'amaguru ukomeye, ahita awushyira mu kazu k'imbeho.
Hazard yahagaritse imyigaragambyo kandi arangije gukina igitaramo cya nyuma akoresheje imbunda y'ibumoso ya Alisson Becker wa Liverpool.
Liverpool igiye kurwana na Napoli mu itsinda rya Champions League ku isaha ya saa tatu z'umugoroba kuri Stadio San Paolo mu mujyi wa Naples mu Butaliyani.
Chelsea izahura na Videoton muri UEFA Europa League saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba i Londres.
Indonesia: Umubare w'abahitanwa na tsunami wiyongereyeho 832
Umubare w'abahitanywe n'umutingito na tsunami muri Indonesia wiyongereye ugera ku 832, nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiza muri Indonesia mu ntangiriro z'iki cyumweru.
Abantu benshi bavugwa ko bafashwe n'amabuye y'inyubako yatewe n'umutingito ukomeye wa 7.5 wabaye ku wa Gatanu, ukaba waratewe n'imiyaga ingana na metero 20, nk'uko umuvugizi Sutopo Purwo Nugroho yabitangaje.
