Koreya ya Ruguru ivuga ko 'nta buryo' ishobora guhagarika ibirwanisho idafite icyizere
Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Koreya ya Ruguru yabwiye Umuryango w'Abibumbye ko ibihano bikomeje, byatumye Amerika irushaho kugirira icyizere Amerika, kandi nta buryo na bumwe igihugu cyashoboraga guhagarika ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi mu mimerere nk'iyo.
Ri Yong Ho yabwiye Koreya ya Ruguru ko mu mwaka ushize yafashe ingamba zikomeye z'ubushake, nko guhagarika igerageza rya kirimbuzi n'ibisasu bya misile, gusenya ikibuga cy'igeragezwa ry'ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga rya kirimbuzi n'ikoranabuhanga rya kirimbuzi.
Yagize ati "Nta gisubizo na kimwe twigeze tubona muri Amerika.
Ati "Ntabwo twizeye ko Amerika izaba ifite umutekano w'igihugu cyacu, kandi mu mimerere nk'iyo, nta buryo bwo guhungabanya ingabo ubwacu ubwa mbere."
Nubwo Koreya ya Ruguru yasubije ibirego bishingiye ku kurwanya kwa Washington mu buryo bwo "kurwanya ibirwanisho ruhonyanganda" aho Koreya ya Ruguru yagombaga guhabwa ingororano igihe yafataga intambwe buhoro buhoro, itangazo rye ryagaragaye ko ridateye kubiri n'ikoreshwa ry'ikoranabuhanga nk'uko Pyongyang yabikoze kera.
Ri yavuze ku itangazo ryatangajwe na Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump mu nama ya mbere hagati ya Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika na Perezida wa Koreya ya Ruguru muri Singapore ku wa 12 Kamena, igihe Kim yasezeranyije ko azakorana na "kugabanya ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi bya Koreya ya Ruguru" mu gihe Trump yasezeranyije ko Koreya ya Ruguru izakomeza umutekano wa Koreya ya Ruguru.
Koreya ya Ruguru ikomeje gushaka iherezo ry'intambara ya Koreya hagati ya 1950 na 53, ariko Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zivuga ko Pyongyang igomba kubanza guhagarika ibitwaro byayo bya kirimbuzi.
Perezida Kagame kandi yasabye ko Koreya ya Ruguru igabanya ibihano bikomeye.
Yagize ati: "Amerika ikomeje "kugabanya ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi" kandi irushaho gushyiraho ibihano kugira ngo intego yayo igere ku ntego mu buryo buhanitse, ndetse no kurwanya "itangazo ry'iherezo ry'intambara."
Ati: "Ikibazo cy'uko ibihano bishobora kutugeza ku mavi yacu ni inzozi z'umusaraba ku bantu batazi kutwitaho.
Ikibazo ni uko ibihano bikomeje kugabanuka mu bitekerezo byacu."
Ri Ri yavuze ko nta migambi ihari iteganyijwe mu nama ya kabiri hagati ya Kim na Trump ivuga ko umuyobozi w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye yagaragaye mu ntangiriro z'icyumweru gishize.
Minisitiri w'Intebe wa Koreya y'Epfo, Moon Jae-in, mu mezi atanu ashize, yagize ati: "Niba ishyaka ry'iki kibazo cy'ingufu za kirimbuzi ryari Koreya y'Epfo, ntabwo Amerika yari kuba Amerika, gukwirakwiza ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi bya Koreya ya Ruguru ntabwo byari kuza mu gihe nk'iki."
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, imvugo ya Ri yari itandukanye cyane n'iyabaye mu mwaka ushize, ubwo yabwiraga Inama rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ya Amerika ko gukurikirana Amerika n'ibisasu bya koreya ya Ruguru byari bidashoboka nyuma y'uko Bwana Evil Perezida Trump yise Kim "umuntu w'iterabwoba" mu gikorwa cyo kwiyahura.
Muri uyu mwaka ku rwego rw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Trump, uherutse gushyira mu gaciro ko "kwica burundu" Koreya ya Ruguru, yashimangiye Kim kubera ubutwari bwe bwo gufata ingamba zo kugabanya ibirwanisho, ariko avuga ko haracyari igikorwa kinini gikwiye gukorwa kandi ko ibihano bigomba gukomeza gushyirwa mu mwanya kugeza igihe Koreya ya Ruguru igaba ibisasu bya kirimbuzi.
Kuri uyu wa Gatatu, Trump yavuze ko nta mwanya yari afite kuri iki kibazo, agira ati "niba bitwara imyaka ibiri, itatu cyangwa itanu - nta cyo bitwaye."
U Bushinwa n'u Burusiya bavuga ko inama y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi igomba guhemba Pyongyang kubera ingamba zafashwe.
Mike Pompeo, Umunyamabanga wa Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika, yabwiye inama y'umutekano ya ONU ku wa Kane ati: "Gushyiraho ibihano bihanishwa n'inama y'umutekano ishinzwe umutekano bigomba gukomeza mu buryo bukomeye kandi bidasubirwaho kugeza igihe tumenye neza ko ibitwaro by'ikoranabuhanga bidasubirwaho."
Guverinoma y'umutekano yatangaje ko kuva mu mwaka wa 2006 ibihano byakorewe Koreya ya Ruguru bigamije guhungabanya umutekano w'ibisasu bya kirimbuzi na missile bya Pyongyang.
Pompeo yahuye na Ri ku ruhande rw'inteko rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, avuga ko mu kwezi gutaha azasura Pyongyang kugira ngo yitegure inama ya kabiri.
Pompeo yasuye Koreya ya Ruguru inshuro eshatu uyu mwaka, ariko urugendo rwe rwa nyuma ntirwagenze neza.
Yavuye muri Pyongyang muri Nyakanga, avuga ko hari iterambere ryakozwe, gusa kuri Koreya ya Ruguru mu masaha make yo kumushinja gukora "ibikenewe nk'ibisanzwe."
Koreya ya Ruguru yasezeranye mu nama yagiranye n'ukwezi muri uku kwezi ko gusenya ahantu hakoreshejwe missile hamwe n'inyubako ya nucleaire, iyo Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zafashe ingamba zihuje n'amategeko.
Yavuze ko Kim yamubwiye "intambwe zihuje n'umutekano" yashakaga, ari intambwe Trump yari yafashe yo gusezerana muri Singapore kandi yiyemeje guhuza imibanire na Washington.
Abanyeshuri ba Rayon Sports bitabiriye imyitozo yo kuruhuka bihagije
Isomo rishya muri Kaminuza ya Harvard uyu mwaka ryatumye abanyeshuri bose barangije amashuri yisumbuye barushaho gusinzira mu rwego rwo kurwanya umuco w'igitsina gore ugenda wiyongera wo kwiga binyuze muri 'kafeyine'.
Akenshi abanyeshuri biga muri kaminuza ya mbere y'isi basanga nta bumenyi bafite ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kwiyitaho ubwabo.
Charles Czeisler, umwarimu w'imiti yo kuryama mu ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya Harvard akaba n'umuhanga mu bitaro bya Brigham na Women's Hospital, yizeye ko ari bwo bwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Yakomeje avuga ko nyuma yo gutangira imyitozo yo kubura ibitotsi byari bimaze gukorwa.
Umukobwa umwe yaje kumbwira ati: "Kuki uyu munsi nsobanurirwa ibi, mu mwaka wanjye mukuru gusa?"
Yagize ati "Nta muntu n'umwe wigeze ambwira ko gusinzira ari ingirakamaro.
Ni ubwa mbere uyu mutoza asobanurira abanyeshuri uko gusinzira neza bifasha mu mikino y'amashuri n'imikino, ndetse n'imibereho myiza muri rusange.
Paul Barreira, umwarimu w'ishuri ry'ubuvuzi ry'i Harvard, akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru w'ubuvuzi muri kaminuza, yavuze ko kaminuza yafashe umwanzuro wo gutangira amasomo nyuma yo kubona abanyeshuri basinziriye cyane mu cyumweru.
Urugendo rurerure rw'isaha rugizwe n'ibikorwa byinshi bijyanye n'ikoranabuhanga.
Mu gice kimwe hari ishusho y'icyumba cyo gusinzira, aho abanyeshuri bakanda ku bikombe bya kafeyine, amabati, abatoza n'ibitabo bagomba kubwirwa ingaruka za kafeyine n'urumuri n'uburyo imikino y'abakinnyi igira ingaruka ku kubura ibitotsi, n'akamaro ko gusinzira.
Mu gice cya kabiri, abagize uruhare mu kubura ibitotsi mu gihe kirekire bashobora kongera ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'umutima, stroke, indwara y'agahinda gakabije n'indwara ya kanseri.
Ikarita y'amakarita y'ishuri, hamwe n'ibishushanyo bihuza, irashishikariza abantu gutekereza ku mikorere yabo ya buri munsi.
Ati "Turabizi ko bitazongera guhindura imyitwarire y'abanyeshuri.
Ati "Turizera ko bafite uburenganzira bwo kumenya ingaruka z'itabi nk'uko ugomba kumenya ingaruka z'ubuzima bw'umuntu uhitamo kunywa itabi.
Yavuze ko umuco w'ubwibone mu "kugabanya ijoro ryose" uracyahari, yongeraho ko ikoranabuhanga rya none n'umuvuduko ukomeje kwiyongera ku banyeshuri bisobanura ko kubura ibitotsi ari ikibazo cyiyongereye.
Avuga ko kugira ngo uryame bihagije, ugomba kuba 'intwaro yihishe' y'umwarimu kugira ngo arwanye stress, guhangayika no guhangayika, ndetse no kwirinda kugabanya ibiro, nk'uko gusinzira bishyira ubwonko mu buryo bw'inzara, bigatuma buhora bushobewe n'inzara.
Raymond So, w'imyaka 19 y'amavuko wo muri California, yize ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima ndetse n'ibinyabuzima, yafashije Porofeseri Czeisler gutegura iri korali, nyuma y'uko yize rimwe mu mashuri ye umwaka ushize mu mwaka wa mbere w'i Harvard.
Avuga ko uyu musore yahise atangira kwiga, amusaba ko yajya kwiga muri kaminuza.
Akomeza avuga ko asaba abanyeshuri bose barangije amashuri yisumbuye gusoza amashuri abanza mbere y'uko binjira mu ishuri.
Professor Czeisler yasabye abanyeshuri gutekereza gushyiraho akamenyetso k'igihe cyo kuryama, ndetse n'igihe cyo kubyuka, no kumenya ingaruka mbi za 'umucyo w'ubururu' zatanzwe n'amashusho ya elegitoronike hamwe n'amatara ya LED, bishobora gukura umuvuduko wawe w'ubushyuhe mu killer, bigatuma ibibazo byo gusinzira.
