Uburyo bwo gukuramo imibiri y'abarwayi mu mubiri bisaba guhindura imiterere y'umubiri
Ushobora guhita ufata 'protein' nyinshi zitera kanseri, hanyuma ukayisubiramo
Urukingo rw'ubushakashatsi rugaragaza ko rutanga umusaruro ku barwayi bafite kanseri zitandukanye.
Umugore umwe wavuwe urukingo, rwigisha abarwayi b'umubiri kumenya uturemangingo tw'umubiri, yabonye kanseri ye y'ibere imaze amezi arenga 18 itagaragara.
Ubu buryo bukubiyemo gukuramo uturemangingo tw'umubiri w'umurwayi, kubuhindura muri laboratoire kugira ngo bashobore "kubona" poroteyine isanzwe ku ndwara nyinshi zitwa HER2, hanyuma bagasubira mu tugingo ngengabuzima.
Porofeseri Jay Berzofsky wo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu kigo cy'indwara ya kanseri i Bethesda muri leta ya Maryland, yagize ati: "Ibi twabonye bigaragaza ko dufite urukingo rutanga icyizere."
