Uburyo nk'ubwo bwo gukuramo uturemangingo tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu barwayi no "kubigisha" uburyo bwo guhangana n'indwara ya kanseri bwakoreshejwe mu kuvura ubwoko bwa leukemia.
