Abashinjacyaha bo muri leta ya New York barimo gushaka igihano cy'urupfu kuri Sayfullo Saipov, ukekwaho kwica abantu umunani mu mujyi wa New York, igihano kidasanzwe kitarakorwa muri leta kuva mu mwaka wa 1953.
Saipov w'imyaka 30 y'amavuko, yavuze ko yakoresheje imodoka yo gukodesha inzu ya Depot kugira ngo akore igitero ku muhanda w'imodoka uri ku muhanda wa West Side Highway uri munsi ya Manhattan, aho abatwara amaguru n'abatwara pikipiki bari mu nzira ye ku itariki ya Oct.
Kugira ngo abashinjacyaha bemeze neza igihano cy'urupfu, bagomba kwemeza ko Saipov yishe abantu umunani bishwe mu buryo budateganywa n'amategeko kandi "bakomeretse bikomeye ku mubiri," nk'uko bitangazwa n'itegeko rigamije gushaka igihano cy'urupfu, ryashyizwe mu Karere k'Amajyepfo ya New York.
Aba bagabo bombi bashobora kuba barakatiwe igihano cy'urupfu nk'uko bivugwa n'urukiko.
Icyumweru kimwe nyuma y'icyo gitero, umucamanza mukuru wo muri leta ya Saipov yashinje ikirego kivuga ko harimo ibirego umunani by'ubwicanyi bwakoreshejwe mu gucukura amabuye y'agaciro, akenshi bikoreshwa n'abashinjacyaha ba leta mu birego by'ubugizi bwa nabi, hamwe n'ibirego by'urugomo no gusenya imodoka.
Abashinjacyaha bavuze ko icyo gitero cyari gikenewe "gutegura neza no gutekereza mbere y'igihe," basobanura uburyo Saipov yabikoraga nk'"ikizira, cy'ubugome n'ubugome."
Yagize ati "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov yakomeretse, yakomerekeje imiryango n'inshuti za Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza na Alejandro Damian Pagnucco.
Batanu muri bo ni abakerarugendo baturutse muri Argentina.
Imyaka ibaye icumi kuva mu ntara y'amajyepfo ya New York haburanishijwe igihano cy'urupfu.
Umushinjacyaha, Khalid Barnes, yahamijwe icyaha cyo kwica abacuruzi babiri b'ibiyobyabwenge, ariko amaherezo yakatiwe igifungo cy'ubuzima muri Nzeri 2009.
Igihano cy'urupfu cyabaye mu mwaka wa 1953 kuri Julius Rosenberg na Ethel Rosenberg, umugabo n'umugore bashyingiranywe biciwe nyuma y'aho bahaniwe icyaha cyo gukurikirana ubutasi bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abasoviyeti mu gihe cy'imyaka ibiri mbere y'intambara y'ubutita.
Bombi barishwe n'inzego z'ubuyobozi bw'inzego z'ibanze ku wa 19 Kamena 1953.
Saipov, ukomoka muri Uzbekistan, yerekanye ko mu minsi n'amezi nyuma y'icyo gitero, nk'uko byatangajwe n'inyandiko z'urukiko.
Yabwiye abanyamakuru ko yishimiye ibyo yakoze, nk'uko polisi ibivuga.
