Yasabye kandi kugaragaza ibendera rya ISIS mu cyumba cye cy'ibitaro, nk'uko polisi ibivuga.
Ntiyigeze aregwa ibyaha by'urubanza rw'amakipe 22.
David Patton, umwe mu badepite ba leta bashyigikiye Saipov, yavuze ko "bababajwe cyane" n'umwanzuro w'ubushinjacyaha.
Yagize ati "Turatekereza ko icyemezo cyo gushaka igihano cy'urupfu aho kwemera gusaba icyaha mu buzima bw'igifungo nta buryo bwo kurekurwa kizakomeza gusa ibyago by'ibibazo kuri buri wese wagize uruhare muri ibi bikorwa."
